#: ../../source/tutorials/quickstart.rst:3
msgid "Quickstart"
msgstr "快速入门"

#: ../../source/tutorials/quickstart.rst:6
msgid "Before proceeding, install Manim and make sure it is running properly by following the steps in :doc:`../installation`. For information on using Manim with Jupyterlab or Jupyter notebook, go to the documentation for the :meth:`IPython magic command <manim.utils.ipython_magic.ManimMagic.manim>`, ``%%manim``."
msgstr "在阅读下列内容之前，请确保您已经安装好了Manim，并按照 :doc:`../installation`中的步骤确认了其可正常运行。关于如何在Jupyterlab或Jupyter notebook中使用Manim，请参阅:meth:`IPython命令<manim.utils.ipython_magic.ManimMagic.manim>` ``%%manim``相关文档。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/quickstart.rst:14
msgid "If you installed Manim in the recommended way, using the Python management tool ``uv``, then you either need to make sure the corresponding virtual environment is activated (follow the instructions printed on running ``uv venv``), or you need to remember to prefix the ``manim`` command in the console with ``uv run``; that is, ``uv run manim ...``."
msgstr "如果您是按照推荐的方式、使用Python管理工具``uv``安装的Manim，那么你需要确保相应的虚拟环境已激活（可参考运行``uv venv``后打印的说明），或者在终端中使用``manim``命令时加上 ``uv run``前缀；即使用``uv run manim ...``命令。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/quickstart.rst:22
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概览"

#: ../../source/tutorials/quickstart.rst:24
msgid "This quickstart guide will lead you through creating a sample project using Manim: an animation engine for precise programmatic animations."
msgstr "Manim是一个用于制作精确、可编程动画的动画引擎，而本快速入门文档将带你使用Manim创建一个示例项目。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/quickstart.rst:27
msgid "First, you will use a command line interface to create a ``Scene``, the class through which Manim generates videos. In the ``Scene`` you will animate a circle. Then you will add another ``Scene`` showing a square transforming into a circle. This will be your introduction to Manim's animation ability. Afterwards, you will position multiple mathematical objects (``Mobject``\\s). Finally, you will learn the ``.animate`` syntax, a powerful feature that animates the methods you use to modify ``Mobject``\\s."
msgstr "首先，您需要通过命令行界面创建一个``Scene``（场景）。Scene是用于生成视频的核心类。在这个``Scene``中，先让一个圆动起来。随后再添加一个 ``Scene``，将一个正方形转换为圆形。这将帮您初步了解 Manim 的动画渲染能力。之后，您将会学习如何摆放多个数学对象（``Mobject``\\s）。并且最后会学到``.animate``语法：该语法是一个非常强大的特性，能够把您用于修改``Mobject``\\s的方法调用直接变成动画。"

