msgstr "您也可以试试其他方法，比如使用``flip``或``shift``，看看会发生什么。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/quickstart.rst:307
msgid "Open ``scene.py``, and add the following code snippet below the ``AnimatedSquareToCircle`` class:"
msgstr "打开``scene.py``，在``AnimatedSquareToCircle``类下添加以下代码："

#: ../../source/tutorials/quickstart.rst:320
msgid "Render ``DifferentRotations`` by running the following command in the command line:"
msgstr "在命令行中运行以下命令，渲染``DifferentRotations``："

#: ../../source/tutorials/quickstart.rst:338
msgid "This ``Scene`` illustrates the quirks of ``.animate``. When using ``.animate``, Manim actually takes a ``Mobject``'s starting state and its ending state and interpolates the two. In the ``AnimatedSquareToCircle`` class, you can observe this when the square rotates: the corners of the square appear to contract slightly as they move into the positions required for the first square to transform into the second one."
msgstr "这个``Scene``展示了``.animate`` 的一些“特性细节”。使用 ``.animate`` 时，Manim实际上会取``Mobject``的起始状态和结束状态，并在两者之间做插值。在``AnimatedSquareToCircle``里，正方形旋转时您可以观察到这一点：正方形的角在移动到目标位置时会略微“收缩”，以从方形变换成圆形。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/quickstart.rst:344
msgid "In ``DifferentRotations``, the difference between ``.animate``'s interpretation of rotation and the ``Rotate`` method is far more apparent. The starting and ending states of a ``Mobject`` rotated 180 degrees are the same, so ``.animate`` tries to interpolate two identical objects and the result is the left square. If you find that your own usage of ``.animate`` is causing similar unwanted behavior, consider using conventional animation methods like the right square, which uses ``Rotate``."
msgstr "在``DifferentRotations``中，``.animate``对旋转的解释与``Rotate``方法之间的差异更加明显。一个``Mobject``旋转180度后的起始状态和结束状态是相同的，因此``.animate``会尝试在两个相同对象之间插值，结果就是左边方形看起来没有旋转。如果您在使用 ``.animate`` 时遇到类似不符合预期的行为，您可以考虑使用传统的动画方法（例如右边方形使用的``Rotate``）。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/quickstart.rst:353
msgid "``Transform`` vs ``ReplacementTransform``"
msgstr "``Transform``与``ReplacementTransform``"

#: ../../source/tutorials/quickstart.rst:355
msgid "The difference between ``Transform`` and ``ReplacementTransform`` is that ``Transform(mob1, mob2)`` transforms the points (as well as other attributes like color) of ``mob1`` into the points/attributes of ``mob2``."
msgstr "``Transform``和``ReplacementTransform``的区别在于：``Transform(mob1, mob2)``会把``mob1`` 的点（以及颜色等其他属性）变换为``mob2``的点/属性。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/quickstart.rst:358
msgid "``ReplacementTransform(mob1, mob2)`` on the other hand literally replaces ``mob1`` on the scene with ``mob2``."
msgstr "而``ReplacementTransform(mob1, mob2)``会在场景中把``mob1``直接替换成``mob2``。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/quickstart.rst:360
msgid "The use of ``ReplacementTransform`` or ``Transform`` is mostly up to personal preference. They can be used to accomplish the same effect, as shown below."
msgstr "该使用``ReplacementTransform``还是``Transform``多数情况下取决于您个人的偏好。如下面所示，它们都可以实现相同效果。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/quickstart.rst:385
msgid "However, in some cases it is more beneficial to use ``Transform``, like when you are transforming several mobjects one after the other. The code below avoids having to keep a reference to the last mobject that was transformed."
msgstr "不过在某些情况下，使用``Transform``会更有优势，比如在需要依次变换多个mobject时。以下代码避免了您总是保存“上一次变换后对象”的引用。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/quickstart.rst:398
msgid "You're done!"
msgstr "完成！"

#: ../../source/tutorials/quickstart.rst:402
msgid "With a working installation of Manim and this sample project under your belt, you're ready to start creating animations of your own.  To learn more about what Manim is doing under the hood, move on to the next tutorial: :doc:`output_and_config`.  For an overview of Manim's features, as well as its configuration and other settings, check out the other :doc:`Tutorials <../tutorials/index>`.  For a list of all available features, refer to the :doc:`../reference` page."
msgstr "当你已成功安装Manim，并完成这个示例项目后，就可以开始创作你自己的动画了。如果您想进一步了解Manim在底层做了什么，请继续阅读下一篇教程：:doc:`output_and_config`。若想快速总览Manim的功能、配置与其他设置，请查看 :doc:`教程总览 <../tutorials/index>`。如需查看全部可用功能，请参考 :doc:`../reference`页面。"
